page.title: 15I HOPE TO BE A DENTIST
page.content:
My name is Annelie Williams and I am 12 years old. I live in {Three Crosses which is about 4 miles away from my school,{Bishopston Comprehensive,}it hasn't been there long just 9 years as it started in 1975 and it is now 1985. I travel to school by bus. When I leave school I hope to be a {dentist}but that is hoping as there are currently a lot of British people out of work. My mum and dad are quite worried about me when I'm older as you could easily get on drugs or some other things which would totally blow your mind. This age is full of computers and videos and is turning out to be a bad place, in the future I hope it gets better.
ANNELIE WILLIAMS 2P
